com.impinj.octane

Class BlockPermalockMask

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.impinj.octane.BlockPermalockMask

  • public class BlockPermalockMask
extends java.lang.Object
    Uses to specify which blocks to permalock. Block permalock sets blocks of memory permanently read-only.
    See Also:
    Gen2 Standard page 94
